This is an upload to a Google Apps Script for a leave form system for a school district with about 150 staff members. The idea was to create a digital leave form system, when there was no budget for such a system. 
Spreadsheets were used to as a way to store the information like a database. This was moved away from in 2023 when a new system was purchased by the district to have staff do digital time clock actions. 
Because leave forms are integral with that the leave form was included in the purchasing of that new system
Each nested branch is a Google Apps Script project with the main section being the file Code.gs which then directs the users to the needed .html file within that same branch. 

